{subhead}Elbox Announces the Spider II USB 2 device{def}
{left}
{pp}
{center}
{image spider_II.iff}
{pp}
{left}
{pp}
USB 2.0 is the next-generation USB (Universal Serial Bus)
interface technology which enables you to connect multiple
devices (such as hubs, printers, skanners, mice, joysticks,
keyboards, external hard drives, CD burners, digital cameras,
etc.) to your Amiga.
{pp}
The minimum hardware configuration for Amiga system is: 68030
turbo card, the Mediator PCI busboard with the Mediator
Multimedia CD and the Voodoo graphic card.
{pp}
The recommended Amiga configuration is: 68060 turbo card, the
Mediator PCI busboard with the Mediator Multimedia CD and the
Voodoo3 graphic card.
{pp}
The Spider II USB 2.0 Hi-Speed PCI card features:
{pp}
    Five USB 2.0 Hi-Speed ports: four external and one internal{p}
    Compatible with both USB 2.0 (480 Mbps) and USB 1.1 (12 Mbps) devices{p}
    Compliant with EHCI, OHCI and PCI 2.2 standards{p}
    All ports can handle high-speed, full-speed and low-speed transaction{p}
    One EHCI (Enhanced Host Controller Interface) and two independent OHCI (Open Host Controller Interface) controllers integrated{p}
    Supports up to 127 downstream USB devices{p}
    Supplies 500 mA power to each USB port{p}
    Supports PCI-Bus Power Management Interface{p}
    Hot Plug Capability
{pp}
Spider II USB 2.0 Hi-Speed card is compatible with all USB
devices compliant with USB 2.0 standard and with all devices
compliant with USB 1.1 standard.
{pp}
The software support for particular USB device is provided by
appropriate Poseidon class driver. All USB devices tested with
Poseidon stack work with Spider.
{pp}
The complete list of tested models of the USB devices (hubs,
keyboards, mice, printers, scanners, ZIPs, HDDs, CDROM drivers
and others) will be available in the Spider USB Devices Guide.
{pp}
Fit the Spider II USB 2.0 PCI card in any free PCI slot.
{pp}
The CD enclosed with the Spider card contains Mediator EHCI
(USB 2.0) and OHCI (USB 1.1) drivers for the Poseidon stack.
{pp}
Spider II USB 2.0 Hi-Speed PCI card Suggested Retail Price
(VAT and local taxes excluded): see Product Price List.
{pp}